data.description: Here is your chance to own a 1977, ranch, 5 BR, 3 BA, 2 car garage, wood fireplace in LR, main floor laundry, master bedroom with 3/4 BA, three bedrooms on the same level, family room located in basement, with two more bedrooms and a 1/2 bath, great storage. New windows including a bay window in LR and new furnace in 2023. This property has a lot to offer and a must see. Backyard butts up to agriculture land - no back neighbors.
